[start section id="20103"]

Mrs. Conatser is a 63-year-old female who underwent a laparoscopic-assisted colectomy with coloanal anastomosis and diverting loop ileostomy on February 5, 2010 for rectal cancer. She is now here for ileostomy takedown. Hypaque enema showed no evidence of a leak. She is now here for reversal of her ileostomy.
Risks, benefits, alternatives, indications, procedure, team approach and advance directives discussed with the patient and she wishes to proceed with surgery.

[end section id="20103"]

