PAST SURGICAL HISTORY
1.  C-section.
2.  Abdominal hysterectomy
3.  History of sinus surgery.
4.  I & D of right neck abscess.
5.  Squamous cell carcinoma of the right cheek on her face removed approximately 2002.
6.  Gastric bypass surgery, unclear whether this for sure was a Roux-en-Y, done laparoscopically in 2005 in Frontier.
7.  Tonsillectomy.
8.  Laparoscopic-assisted proctectomy with coloanal anastomosis and diverting loop ileostomy  (February 5, 2010 Dr. Snyder)

